# Job Application Tracker (CLI)

A simple command-line tool to track job applications - add, view, update, delete, and filter entries, with data saved between sessions.

## Features
- Add new job applications (company, role, status)
- View all applications in a numbered list
- Update an application's status
- Delete an application (with confirmation)
- Filter applications by status
- Data persists automatically to a local JSON file

## Usage
Run `python3 tracker_cli.py` and follow the menu prompts.

## Built with
Python (json module for data persistence)   

## Future improvements
- Command-line arguments (e.g. `tracker.py add --company Google`) instead of a menu
- Sorting applications by date applied
- Filtering by company